00:16:00,673 --> 00:16:04,934
you a better rating you're not trying to say some users can't rank your game and

324
00:16:04,934 --> 00:16:06,774
not you're just putting the prompt

325
00:16:06,774 --> 00:16:11,576
at a time that users are likely enjoying the experience and you can work with

