00:16:42,666 --> 00:16:45,867
connections so you're going to need a disclosure or it's going to be risky to

334
00:16:45,867 --> 00:16:46,847
not have a disclosure.

335
00:16:48,046 --> 00:16:52,809
Second takeaway is the FTC hasn't yet enforced against divergent prompting,

