00:25:54,504 --> 00:25:55,544
have two answers for you.

512
00:25:56,511 --> 00:26:00,213
First is the complicated, but probably the best answer,

513
00:26:00,213 --> 00:26:03,816
which is every time you have a churn of more than 50%,

