00:31:52,436 --> 00:31:56,338
time, maybe once a week, maybe once every two weeks, check in, and then if you see a

626
00:31:56,338 --> 00:31:59,960
problem with an influencer, go back and look at all the rest of their posts.

627
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:07,784
So our takeaways here are regular, robust monitoring is a best practice.

